Tag the repository with the next semantic version

USAGE
  nsv tag [FLAGS] [PATH]...

FLAGS
  -h, --help
          help for tag

  -m, --message <MESSAGE>
          a custom message for the tag

GLOBAL FLAGS
      --log-level <LOG-LEVEL>
          set the logging verbosity

          [default: info]

      --no-color
          disable colored output

      --no-log
          disable all log output
